Reproducing the figures

Load libraries

library(scMisc)
library(Seurat)
library(ggplot2)
library(qs)
library(sessioninfo)

Figure 1

UMAP of all cells (Figure 1B)

Download data

options(timeout = 3600)
if (!file.exists("umap_figure.qs")) {
    download.file(
        "https://zenodo.org/records/14226219/files/umap_figure.qs?download=1",
        "umap_figure.qs"
    )
}

Load data and plot

umap_figure <- qread("umap_figure.qs")
DimPlot(
    umap_figure,
    reduction = "umap.scvi.full",
    pt.size = .1,
    alpha = .1,
    cols = umap_figure@misc$cluster_col,
    label = TRUE,
    raster = FALSE
) +
    NoLegend() +
    theme_rect() +
    xlab("UMAP_1") +
    ylab("UMAP_2")

Figure 2

UMAP immune cells (Figure 2A)

Download data.

options(timeout = 3600)
if (!file.exists("ic_umap_figure.qs")) {
    download.file(
        "https://zenodo.org/records/14226219/files/umap_figure.qs?download=1",
        "ic_umap_figure.qs"
    )
}

Load data and plot.

ic_umap_figure <- qread("ic_umap_figure.qs")
    DimPlot(
        ic_umap_figure,
        reduction = "umap.rpca",
        pt.size = .1,
        alpha = .3,
        cols = ic_umap_figure@misc$ic_cluster_col,
        label = TRUE,
        raster = FALSE
    ) +
    theme_rect() +
    NoLegend() +
    xlab("UMAP1") +
    ylab("UMAP2")
